{"tid":1991043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【#商業熱話】Adidas首季少賺九成，預期下季虧損","createTime":"2020-04-27T07:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T07:19:36.000Z","uid":324034,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d49d903af400d8f5f3c00e6363316ab2de2cdb2","tid":1991043,"uid":324034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T07:12:58.000Z","msg":"【#商業熱話】Adidas首季少賺九成，預期下季虧損<br />\n<br />\n歐洲最大體育用品公司Adidas公佈首季業績，首季經營溢利大跌93%至6,500萬歐元，遜市場預期，銷售下跌19%至47.53億歐元，同樣低過預期。Adidas首席執行官Kasper Rorsted表示，由於未知店鋪需要關閉多久時間，因此無法提供全年業績預測。<br />\n<br />\nAdidas預計，第二季新型冠狀病毒疫情帶來的衝擊更大，銷售將大跌逾40%。Adidas更預期，下季業績將會出現虧損。公司表示，目前公司在全球有超過7成店舖關閉，雖然首季網上銷售增長35%，但僅能抵消部分的銷售損失。<br />\n<br />\nAdidas的任何復甦都取決於中國和網上購物。在本季度的前三週，大中華區的銷售額一直逐步改善。儘管如此，這不能抵消歐洲、北美、南美、俄羅斯以及亞洲其他地區店鋪的關閉。<br />\n<br />\n消息來源：Bloomberg<br />\n製圖／文字：Business Digest<br />\n網站文章：<a href=\"https://businessdigest.io/article/商業熱話/3669/adidas/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessdigest.io%2Farticle%2F%E5%95%86%E6%A5%AD%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F3669%2Fadidas%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4RAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=15718b92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessdigest.io/article/商業熱話/3669/adidas/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自從劉亦菲做代言人後，我發誓，我全家永遠唔會買任何亚迪达斯嘅產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3235c5c1357e7661d8d1ee3046e852514e6e462","tid":1991043,"uid":34410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"我以前淨係買adidas既鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家轉買新把撚算 見到劉亦菲唔開胃"},{"pid":"259433588069cd7cdd97c7baeeaef0353c2f9d1e","tid":1991043,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3235c5c1357e7661d8d1ee3046e852514e6e462","tid":1991043,"uid":34410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"我以前淨係買adidas既鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家轉買新把撚算 見到劉亦菲唔開胃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"球星支那樂係咪仲代言緊"}]}